      <title>github-Blog</title>
      <link href="/2020/04/24/github-Blog/"/>
      <url>/2020/04/24/github-Blog/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="准备"><a href="#准备" class="headerlink" title="准备"></a>准备</h2><h3 id="安装git、nodejs"><a href="#安装git、nodejs" class="headerlink" title="安装git、nodejs"></a>安装git、nodejs</h3><p>git已安装（<del>不是自己安的，先不做赘述</del>）</p><h4 id="nodejs"><a href="#nodejs" class="headerlink" title="nodejs"></a><strong>nodejs</strong></h4><p><strong>下载软件包</strong></p><p><a href="https://nodejs.org/dist/v12.16.2/node-v12.16.2-linux-x64.tar.xz" target="_blank" rel="noopener">nodejs下载</a></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ wget https://nodejs.org/dist/v12.16.2/node-v12.16.2-linux-x64.tar.xz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>解压</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ tar -xvf node-v12.16.2-linux-x64.tar.xz -C /opt/software/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>etc/profile</strong></p><p>增加环境变量</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">export NODEJS_HOME&#x3D;&#x2F;opt&#x2F;software&#x2F;node-v12.16.2-linux-x64</span><br><span class="line">export PATH&#x3D;$PATH:NODEJS_HOME&#x2F;bin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>sourse /etc/profile</code></p><p><strong>测试</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ node -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="hexo"><a href="#hexo" class="headerlink" title="hexo"></a>hexo</h4><p><strong>安装</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>初始化</strong></p><p>创建一个工作路径 <em>(可以在nodejs内，也可以在nodejs外)</em></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ mkdir hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>进入路径=&gt;初始化</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable">$cd</span> hexo</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$hexo</span> init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>测试</strong></p><p>开启服务器</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看4000端口</p><p><a href="https://localhost:4000" target="_blank" rel="noopener">localhost:4000</a></p><h4 id="部署到github"><a href="#部署到github" class="headerlink" title="部署到github"></a>部署到github</h4><p><strong>创建新的仓库</strong></p><p><strong>给仓库添加ssh key</strong></p><p><strong>为git 配置github信息</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git config --global user.email <span class="string">"xxxxx@xxx.com"</span></span><br><span class="line">$ git config --global user.name <span class="string">"xxxx"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>修改hexo配置</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ vi _config.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>deploy的配置</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repository: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;xxx&#x2F;xxx.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>部署</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo g -d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="查看效果"><a href="#查看效果" class="headerlink" title="查看效果"></a>查看效果</h4><p><a href="https://xxx.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
